 six months by the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI).\", \"from\": 306, \"to\": 537, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 435, \"end\": 440, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.7004377701690908e-14, \"text\": \"Paris\", \"types\": [\"Q486972\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Paris\"}, {\"begin\": 532, \"end\": 535, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Britain'sjoint-most decorated female Olympianand\", \"from\": 330, \"to\": 378}, {\"ngram\": \"her fourthGames\", \"from\": 416, \"to\": 431}, {\"ngram\": \"six months\", \"from\": 466, \"to\": 476}, {\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 480, \"to\": 508}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 513, \"to\": 530}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In her statement, Dujardin claimed she made an 'error of judgement' during a coaching session four years agoand is 'deeply ashamed' of her actions.\", \"from\": 539, \"to\": 686, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"her statement\", \"from\": 542, \"to\": 555}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 557, \"to\": 565}, {\"ngram\": \"an 'error\", \"from\": 583, \"to\": 592}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 596, \"to\": 605}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 614, \"to\": 632}, {\"ngram\": \"four years agoand\", \"from\": 633, \"to\": 650}, {\"ngram\": \"her actions\", \"from\": 674, \"to\": 685}]}, {\"sentence\": \"The video - shown for the first time onITV'sGood Morning Britainon Wednesday - has been sent to the FEI and the British Equestrian Federation, while a complaint of animal cruelty has been filed against Dujardin by Stephan Wensing, a Dutch equine lawyer, this week.\", \"from\": 688, \"to\": 952, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 788, \"end\": 791, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 800, \"end\": 829, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 902, \"end\": 909, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephan_Fox\", \"score\": 0.5595278598059854, \"rank\": 0.4452779111169081, \"text\": \"Stephan\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephan_Fox\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Stephan_Fox\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the first time\", \"from\": 710, \"to\": 724}, {\"ngram\": \"onITV'sGood Morning Britainon\", \"from\": 725, \"to\": 754}, {\"ngram\": \"a complaint\", \"from\": 837, \"to\": 848}, {\"ngram\": \"animal cruelty\", \"from\": 852, \"to\": 866}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 890, \"to\": 898}, {\"ngram\": \"a Dutch equine lawyer\", \"from\": 919, \"to\": 940}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Wensing, who is acting on behalf of an anonymous client, revealed that in the video which was recorded during a training event in the UK, Dujardin 'hit the horse many times' in order to 'lift its legs further'.\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 1164, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1088, \"end\": 1090, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"score\": 0.9232306402964482, \"rank\": 0.08315294438873723, \"text\": \"UK\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/United_Kingdom\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wensing\", \"from\": 954, \"to\": 961}, {\"ngram\": \"behalf\", \"from\": 980, \"to\": 986}, {\"ngram\": \"an anonymous client\", \"from\": 990, \"to\": 1009}, {\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 1028, \"to\": 1037}, {\"ngram\": \"a training event\", \"from\": 1064, \"to\": 1080}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 1092, \"to\": 1100}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 1106, \"to\": 1115}, {\"ngram\": \"order\", \"from\": 1131, \"to\": 1136}, {\"ngram\": \"its legs\", \"from\": 1146, \"to\": 1154}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was a sponsored guest lesson, of which my client was the sponsor and went to watch.\", \"from\": 1166, \"to\": 1253, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a sponsored guest lesson\", \"from\": 1174, \"to\": 1198}, {\"ngram\": \"my client\", \"from\": 1209, \"to\": 1218}, {\"ngram\": \"the sponsor\", \"from\": 1223, \"to\": 1234}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A girl was given a lesson with her horse, in the presence of her mother,' Wensing toldHoefslag.\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1349, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A girl\", \"from\": 1254, \"to\": 1260}, {\"ngram\": \"a lesson\", \"from\": 1271, \"to\": 1279}, {\"ngram\": \"her horse\", \"from\": 1285, \"to\": 1294}, {\"ngram\": \"the presence\", \"from\": 1299, \"to\": 1311}, {\"ngram\": \"her mother\", \"from\": 1315, \"to\": 1325}, {\"ngram\": \"toldHoefslag\", \"from\": 1336, \"to\": 1348}]}, {\"sentence\": \"A video has emerged from four years ago which shows me making an error of judgement during a coaching session.\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1461, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"A video\", \"from\": 1351, \"to\": 1358}, {\"ngram\": \"an error\", \"from\": 1413, \"to\": 1421}, {\"ngram\": \"judgement\", \"from\": 1425, \"to\": 1434}, {\"ngram\": \"a coaching session\", \"from\": 1442, \"to\": 1460}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Understandably, the International Federation for Equestrian Sports (FEI) is investigating and I have made the decision to withdraw from all competition - including the Paris Olympics - while this process takes place.\", \"from\": 1463, \"to\": 1679, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1531, \"end\": 1534, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the International Federation\", \"from\": 1479, \"to\": 1507}, {\"ngram\": \"Equestrian Sports\", \"from\": 1512, \"to\": 1529}, {\"ngram\": \"the decision\", \"from\": 1569, \"to\": 1581}, {\"ngram\": \"all competition\", \"from\": 1599, \"to\": 1614}, {\"ngram\": \"the Paris Olympics\", \"from\": 1627, \"to\": 1645}, {\"ngram\": \"this process\", \"from\": 1654, \"to\": 1666}, {\"ngram\": \"place\", \"from\": 1673, \"to\": 1678}]}, {\"sentence\": \"What happened was completely out of character and does not reflect how I train my horses or coach my pupils, however there is no excuse.\", \"from\": 1681, \"to\": 1817, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"character\", \"from\": 1717, \"to\": 1726}, {\"ngram\": \"my horses\", \"from\": 1760, \"to\": 1769}, {\"ngram\": \"my pupils\", \"from\": 1779, \"to\": 1788}, {\"ngram\": \"no excuse\", \"from\": 1807, \"to\": 1816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am deeply ashamed and should have set a better example in that moment.\", \"from\": 1818, \"to\": 1890, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a better example\", \"from\": 1858, \"to\": 1874}, {\"ngram\": \"that moment\", \"from\": 1878, \"to\": 1889}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I am sincerely sorry for my actions and devastated that I have let everyone down, including Team GB, fans and sponsors.\", \"from\": 1892, \"to\": 2011, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 1984, \"end\": 1991, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"score\": 0.9999997611503489, \"rank\": 2.388500655896921e-07, \"text\": \"Team GB\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Team_GB\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"my actions\", \"from\": 1917, \"to\": 1927}, {\"ngram\": \"everyone\", \"from\": 1959, \"to\": 1967}, {\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 1993, \"to\": 1997}, {\"ngram\": \"sponsors\", \"from\": 2002, \"to\": 2010}]}, {\"sentence\": \"I will cooperate fully with the FEI, British Equestrian Federation and British Dressage during their investigations, and will not be commenting further until the process is complete.\", \"from\": 2013, \"to\": 2195, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2045, \"end\": 2048, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 2050, \"end\": 2079, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Equestrian Federation\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Equestrian_Federation\"}, {\"begin\": 2084, \"end\": 2100, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"their investigations\", \"from\": 2108, \"to\": 2128}, {\"ngram\": \"the process\", \"from\": 2171, \"to\": 2182}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Charlotte Dujardin, 23rd July 2024.\", \"from\": 2197, \"to\": 2232, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2197, \"end\": 2215, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"Charlotte Dujardin\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Dujardin\"}], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'During the lesson, Charlotte hit the horse of the student many times in the gallop to lift its legs further.\", \"from\": 2234, \"to\": 2343, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2254, \"end\": 2263, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"score\": 0.5495379110162433, \"rank\": 0.8197105179341593, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the lesson\", \"from\": 2242, \"to\": 2252}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 2268, \"to\": 2277}, {\"ngram\": \"the student\", \"from\": 2281, \"to\": 2292}, {\"ngram\": \"the gallop\", \"from\": 2307, \"to\": 2317}, {\"ngram\": \"its legs\", \"from\": 2326, \"to\": 2334}]}, {\"sentence\": \"This while the horse was more than well-behaved.\", \"from\": 2344, \"to\": 2392, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 2355, \"to\": 2364}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'My client already thought at the time that it was actually impossible, but Charlotte was an Olympic champion, so she would know how to do it.\", \"from\": 2394, \"to\": 2536, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2470, \"end\": 2479, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"score\": 0.5495379110162433, \"rank\": 0.8197105179341593, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My client\", \"from\": 2395, \"to\": 2404}, {\"ngram\": \"the time\", \"from\": 2424, \"to\": 2432}, {\"ngram\": \"an Olympic champion\", \"from\": 2484, \"to\": 2503}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Charlotte also acted as if it was the most normal thing in the world.\", \"from\": 2538, \"to\": 2608, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2539, \"end\": 2548, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"score\": 0.5495379110162433, \"rank\": 0.8197105179341593, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the most normal thing\", \"from\": 2573, \"to\": 2594}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 2598, \"to\": 2607}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Later she realised that this was unacceptable.\", \"from\": 2609, \"to\": 2655, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"'When more eliminations followed after similar videos with other riders, she decided to do something with it.\", \"from\": 2657, \"to\": 2766, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more eliminations\", \"from\": 2663, \"to\": 2680}, {\"ngram\": \"similar videos\", \"from\": 2696, \"to\": 2710}, {\"ngram\": \"other riders\", \"from\": 2716, \"to\": 2728}, {\"ngram\": \"something\", \"from\": 2748, \"to\": 2757}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'It was only on Saturday that I got the green light to send it to the FEI.\", \"from\": 2768, \"to\": 2842, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2838, \"end\": 2841, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Saturday\", \"from\": 2784, \"to\": 2792}, {\"ngram\": \"the green light\", \"from\": 2804, \"to\": 2819}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She did not dare to do that before, because there is an enormous culture of fear.\", \"from\": 2843, \"to\": 2924, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"an enormous culture\", \"from\": 2896, \"to\": 2915}, {\"ngram\": \"fear\", \"from\": 2919, \"to\": 2923}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She also has no interests in other riders or teams, but could not bear Charlotte to win medals at the Games.'\", \"from\": 2925, \"to\": 3034, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 2996, \"end\": 3005, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"score\": 0.5495379110162433, \"rank\": 0.8197105179341593, \"text\": \"Charlotte\", \"types\": [\"Q729\", \"Q5\", \"Q215627\", \"Q19088\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Charlotte_Flair\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"no interests\", \"from\": 2938, \"to\": 2950}, {\"ngram\": \"other riders\", \"from\": 2954, \"to\": 2966}, {\"ngram\": \"teams\", \"from\": 2970, \"to\": 2975}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3013, \"to\": 3019}, {\"ngram\": \"the Games\", \"from\": 3023, \"to\": 3032}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Speaking on Good Morning Britain, Wensing added: 'My client was present at this training and in the beginning she was not really in that [much] shock because she was thinking it was training by the best rider of the world and everything she presents, everything she will do, is okay.\", \"from\": 3036, \"to\": 3319, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Good Morning Britain\", \"from\": 3048, \"to\": 3068}, {\"ngram\": \"Wensing\", \"from\": 3070, \"to\": 3077}, {\"ngram\": \"My client\", \"from\": 3086, \"to\": 3095}, {\"ngram\": \"this training\", \"from\": 3111, \"to\": 3124}, {\"ngram\": \"the beginning\", \"from\": 3132, \"to\": 3145}, {\"ngram\": \"[much] shock\", \"from\": 3173, \"to\": 3185}, {\"ngram\": \"the best rider\", \"from\": 3230, \"to\": 3244}, {\"ngram\": \"the world\", \"from\": 3248, \"to\": 3257}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3262, \"to\": 3272}, {\"ngram\": \"everything\", \"from\": 3287, \"to\": 3297}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'But after that she was was thinking, \\\"This is not okay, this is animal abuse, I do not know what to do\\\", and then she has spoken with a few people and they all advised her to not do anything because they come after you.\", \"from\": 3321, \"to\": 3541, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"animal abuse\", \"from\": 3386, \"to\": 3398}, {\"ngram\": \"a few people\", \"from\": 3456, \"to\": 3468}, {\"ngram\": \"anything\", \"from\": 3504, \"to\": 3512}]}, {\"sentence\": \"There is a big fear and she was not brave enough.\", \"from\": 3542, \"to\": 3591, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"a big fear\", \"from\": 3551, \"to\": 3561}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And then more riders were suspended last year, from Denmark etcetera, and then she got more courage so this is not a political thing.\", \"from\": 3593, \"to\": 3727, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 3646, \"end\": 3653, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"score\": 0.9999990729106435, \"rank\": 9.214495115736661e-07, \"text\": \"Denmark\", \"types\": [\"Q6256\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/Denmark\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"more riders\", \"from\": 3603, \"to\": 3614}, {\"ngram\": \"more courage\", \"from\": 3681, \"to\": 3693}, {\"ngram\": \"a political thing\", \"from\": 3709, \"to\": 3726}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She has nothing to do with medals.\", \"from\": 3728, \"to\": 3762, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 3736, \"to\": 3743}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3755, \"to\": 3761}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Also, your life does not depend on medals and a horse cannot speak.\", \"from\": 3763, \"to\": 3830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"your life\", \"from\": 3769, \"to\": 3778}, {\"ngram\": \"medals\", \"from\": 3798, \"to\": 3804}, {\"ngram\": \"a horse\", \"from\": 3809, \"to\": 3816}]}, {\"sentence\": \"Somebody has to stand up for the horses.\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3871, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Somebody\", \"from\": 3831, \"to\": 3839}, {\"ngram\": \"the horses\", \"from\": 3860, \"to\": 3870}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The most important thing is: this is not an incident.\", \"from\": 3873, \"to\": 3927, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"The most important thing\", \"from\": 3874, \"to\": 3898}, {\"ngram\": \"an incident\", \"from\": 3915, \"to\": 3926}]}, {\"sentence\": \"My client has seen this more times.'\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3964, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My client\", \"from\": 3928, \"to\": 3937}]}, {\"sentence\": \"On Dujardin's claim that it was an isolated incident, Wensing replied: 'My client is saying that this is the standard way of training horses at Dujardin's place.\", \"from\": 3966, \"to\": 4127, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Dujardin's claim\", \"from\": 3969, \"to\": 3985}, {\"ngram\": \"an isolated incident\", \"from\": 3998, \"to\": 4018}, {\"ngram\": \"Wensing\", \"from\": 4020, \"to\": 4027}, {\"ngram\": \"My client\", \"from\": 4038, \"to\": 4047}, {\"ngram\": \"the standard way\", \"from\": 4071, \"to\": 4087}, {\"ngram\": \"training horses\", \"from\": 4091, \"to\": 4106}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin's place\", \"from\": 4110, \"to\": 4126}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'She explained also, before the training, you must be aware of the fact, that she did not film it before she started whipping.\", \"from\": 4129, \"to\": 4255, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the training\", \"from\": 4157, \"to\": 4169}, {\"ngram\": \"the fact\", \"from\": 4192, \"to\": 4200}]}, {\"sentence\": \"She was already whipping the horse.\", \"from\": 4256, \"to\": 4291, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 4281, \"to\": 4290}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'And she explained, \\\"I want to lift up the legs and canter\\\", so it was nothing to do with dressage, it was a canter exercise, and lifting up by beating the horse.\", \"from\": 4293, \"to\": 4455, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the legs\", \"from\": 4332, \"to\": 4340}, {\"ngram\": \"canter\", \"from\": 4345, \"to\": 4351}, {\"ngram\": \"nothing\", \"from\": 4364, \"to\": 4371}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 4383, \"to\": 4391}, {\"ngram\": \"a canter exercise\", \"from\": 4400, \"to\": 4417}, {\"ngram\": \"the horse\", \"from\": 4445, \"to\": 4454}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you look to the video, it also looks like this is the normal way for Dujardin.\", \"from\": 4457, \"to\": 4539, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"the video\", \"from\": 4473, \"to\": 4482}, {\"ngram\": \"the normal way\", \"from\": 4511, \"to\": 4525}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 4530, \"to\": 4538}]}, {\"sentence\": \"But it is not normal.'\", \"from\": 4540, \"to\": 4562, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": []}, {\"sentence\": \"Wensing said his client had received plenty of comments from 'crazy' fans of Dujardin, defending the actions of their 'superstar'.\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4694, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"Wensing\", \"from\": 4564, \"to\": 4571}, {\"ngram\": \"his client\", \"from\": 4577, \"to\": 4587}, {\"ngram\": \"plenty\", \"from\": 4601, \"to\": 4607}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 4611, \"to\": 4619}, {\"ngram\": \"'crazy' fans\", \"from\": 4625, \"to\": 4637}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 4641, \"to\": 4649}, {\"ngram\": \"the actions\", \"from\": 4661, \"to\": 4672}, {\"ngram\": \"their 'superstar\", \"from\": 4676, \"to\": 4692}]}, {\"sentence\": \"He continued: 'My client hired me a few weeks ago and she was still doubting every day because she is really afraid of victim blaming.\", \"from\": 4696, \"to\": 4830, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"My client\", \"from\": 4711, \"to\": 4720}, {\"ngram\": \"victim blaming\", \"from\": 4815, \"to\": 4829}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'If you look to all the thousands of comments, you already see that this is happening because this affects a superstar and a superstar has so, so many fans and they stand up for her.\", \"from\": 4832, \"to\": 5014, \"entities\": [], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"all the thousands\", \"from\": 4848, \"to\": 4865}, {\"ngram\": \"comments\", \"from\": 4869, \"to\": 4877}, {\"ngram\": \"a superstar\", \"from\": 4939, \"to\": 4950}, {\"ngram\": \"a superstar\", \"from\": 4955, \"to\": 4966}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'Some [fans] are crazy but that's how it works in dressage, so my client had so much fear that this weekend, last weekend, she decided to admit the complaint to the FEI.'\", \"from\": 5016, \"to\": 5186, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5181, \"end\": 5184, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"fans\", \"from\": 5023, \"to\": 5027}, {\"ngram\": \"dressage\", \"from\": 5066, \"to\": 5074}, {\"ngram\": \"my client\", \"from\": 5079, \"to\": 5088}, {\"ngram\": \"so much fear\", \"from\": 5093, \"to\": 5105}, {\"ngram\": \"the complaint\", \"from\": 5160, \"to\": 5173}]}, {\"sentence\": \"In its statement, the FEI revealed that Dujardin had engaged 'in conduct contrary to the principles of horse welfare' during the training session at a private stable.\", \"from\": 5188, \"to\": 5354, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5210, \"end\": 5213, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"its statement\", \"from\": 5191, \"to\": 5204}, {\"ngram\": \"Dujardin\", \"from\": 5228, \"to\": 5236}, {\"ngram\": \"conduct\", \"from\": 5253, \"to\": 5260}, {\"ngram\": \"the principles\", \"from\": 5273, \"to\": 5287}, {\"ngram\": \"horse welfare\", \"from\": 5291, \"to\": 5304}, {\"ngram\": \"the training session\", \"from\": 5313, \"to\": 5333}, {\"ngram\": \"a private stable\", \"from\": 5337, \"to\": 5353}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'The FEI has officially announced the provisional suspension of British Dressage athlete Charlotte Dujardin (FEI ID: 10028440) for a period of six months, effective immediately from the date of notification, 23 July 2024,' the statement from the FEI read.\", \"from\": 5356, \"to\": 5611, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5361, \"end\": 5364, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}, {\"begin\": 5420, \"end\": 5436, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/British_Dressage\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 0.0, \"text\": \"British Dressage\", \"types\": [\"Q43229\", \"Q24229398\"], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.