ticipate in the upcoming Paris 2024 Olympic Games or any other events under the jurisdiction of the FEI.\", \"from\": 5613, \"to\": 5761, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5757, \"end\": 5760, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"This decision\", \"from\": 5614, \"to\": 5627}, {\"ngram\": \"the upcoming Paris 2024 Olympic Games\", \"from\": 5669, \"to\": 5706}, {\"ngram\": \"any other events\", \"from\": 5710, \"to\": 5726}, {\"ngram\": \"the jurisdiction\", \"from\": 5733, \"to\": 5749}]}, {\"sentence\": \"'During this period of suspension, she is prohibited from participating in any activities related to competitions or events under the jurisdiction of the FEI or any competition or event under the jurisdiction of a National Federation (NF).\", \"from\": 5763, \"to\": 6002, \"entities\": [{\"begin\": 5917, \"end\": 5920, \"title\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"score\": 1.0, \"rank\": 1.953834564193247e-51, \"text\": \"FEI\", \"types\": [], \"wikid\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\", \"dbpedia\": \"http://dbpedia.org/resource/International_Federation_for_Equestrian_Sports\"}], \"noun_phrases\": [{\"ngram\": \"this period\", \"from\": 5771, \"to\": 5782}, {\"ngram\": \"suspension\", \"from\": 5786, \"to\": 5796}, {\"ngram\": \"any activities\", \"from\": 5838, \"to\": 5852}, {\"ngram\": \"competitions\", \"from\": 5864, \"to\": 5876}, {\"ngram\": \"events\", \"from\": 5880, \"to\": 5886}, {\"ngram\": \"the jurisdiction\", \"from\": 5893, \"to\": 5909}, {\"ngram\": \"any competition\", \"from\": 5924, \"to\": 5939}, {\"ngram\":